Eduardo Fajardo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eduardo_Fajardo 0 Eduardo Fajardo (born 14 August 1924) is a Galician film actor born in Pontevedra, Spain. He appeared in more than 160 films between 1947 and 2002. He started the Almeria Walk of Fame, where he received an star on 11 April 2012 due to his intervention in 7th Cavalry and Django.
